mozilla-firefox 2.0.0.8 doesn't seem to want to build with canvas support. 

liboil cannot be build with hyper-optimization, else the resulting library can 
cause segfaults. (Noticed with gstreamer plugins)

libdvdcss: With tetex installed, building may stall on the documentation on 
Slackware 12; it stalls with some unicode problems.  

NetworkManager 0.7 (due soon as of October 14,2007) obsoletes dhcddb.
